"sahadhammena suniggahitaṃ niggahetvā sappāṭihāriyaṃ dhammaṃ desenti."
msgstr "Today you do have such nun disciples."

msgctxt "dn16:132.4"
msgid ""
"Parinibbātu dāni, bhante, bhagavā, parinibbātu sugato, parinibbānakālo dāni, "
