msgid "Dhammiyā kathāya sandassemi samādapemi samuttejemi sampahaṃsemi."
msgstr "I educated, encouraged, fired up, and inspired them with a Dharma talk."

msgctxt "dn16:152.26"
msgid "Bhāsamānañca maṃ na jānanti:"
msgstr "But when I spoke they didn’t know:"

msgctxt "dn16:152.27"
msgid "‘ko nu kho ayaṃ bhāsati devo vā manusso vā’ti?"
msgstr "‘Who is this that speaks? Is it a god or a human?’"

