msgid "Antarahitañca maṃ na jānanti:"
msgstr "But when I vanished they didn’t know: "

msgctxt "dn16:152.30"
msgid "‘ko nu kho ayaṃ antarahito devo vā manusso vā’ti?"
msgstr "‘Who was that who vanished? Was it a god or a human?’"

msgctxt "dn16:152.31"
msgid "Imā kho, ānanda, aṭṭha parisā."
msgstr "These are the eight assemblies."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn16:153.1"
msgid "18. Aṭṭhaabhibhāyatana"
msgstr "Eight Dimensions of Mastery"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="129"></a><a class="wp" id="wp3.24"></a>
msgctxt "dn16:154.1"
msgid "Aṭṭha kho imāni, ānanda, abhibhāyatanāni."
msgstr "Ānanda, there are these eight dimensions of mastery."

msgctxt "dn16:154.2"
msgid "Katamāni aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight? "

#. <a class="wp" id="wp3.25"></a>
msgctxt "dn16:154.3"
msgid ""
"Ajjhattaṃ rūpasaññī eko bahiddhā rūpāni passati parittāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni."
msgstr ""
"Not perceiving form internally, they see visions externally, limited, both "
"pretty and ugly."

msgctxt "dn16:154.4"
msgid "‘Tāni abhibhuyya jānāmi passāmī’ti evaṃsaññī hoti."
msgstr "Mastering them, they perceive: ‘I know and see.’ "

msgctxt "dn16:154.5"
msgid "Idaṃ paṭhamaṃ abhibhāyatanaṃ."
msgstr "This is the first dimension of mastery."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="130"></a><a class="wp" id="wp3.26"></a>
